- [Till](till.md) - Till loops
- [Till Syntax](till_syntax.md) - Complete syntax
- [For](for.md) - For loops
- [Loop](loop.md) - Infinite loops

---

**Remember**: Loop direction = **up (default) or down** - use `down` for countdown, `by` for custom steps!

