## Optional Blocks

### `then` is Optional

```aria
// Only care about early exit case
when(condition) {
    if (found) {
        break;
    }
}
end {
    print("Found!");
}
// No then block needed
```

### `end` is Optional

```aria
// Only care about normal completion
when(condition) {
    process();
}
then {
    print("All done!");
}
// No end block needed
```

### Both Optional (Just a Loop)

```aria
// Equivalent to while loop
when(condition) {
    doWork();
```

