## Error Handling Pattern

### Combining with Result Types

```aria
when(attempts < maxAttempts) {
    result<Connection>:result = tryConnect();

    if (result.is_error) {
        logError(result.err);
        attempts++;
    } else {
        useConnection(raw(result));
        break;  // Success
    }
}
then {
    fail("Failed to connect after &{maxAttempts} attempts");
}
end {
    pass(connection);
```

